verse = \lyricmode {
  You turn us back to dust when life is end -- ed,
for so you in these ver -- y words com -- man -- ded:
\"Re -- turn to dust, O mor -- tals.\" Thus we per -- ish.
Brief is our life, and vain the things we cher -- ish.
A thou -- sand of our years are in your sight
a day gone by, a watch that ends the night.
}
